name: DEN_nancey
description:
another look i always loved, only ever knew her as Nancey but possibly better know as miriama kunkelova but such a sublime sweet face. Its a shame I haven't managed to capture the mole above her lip as that is the part I like most.

Thanks to feedback from @HaikenEdge I have changed my demos to better reflect the model though I know some of mine really don't do a good job.
